name: @fluentui/react-icons
description: Fluent System Icons are a collection of familiar, friendly, and modern icons from Microsoft.

scripts.create16: touch ./example/icon16.tsx && rm ./example/icon16.tsx && touch ./example/icon16.tsx && cat ./example/exampleStart.tsx >> ./example/icon16.tsx && ls -1 ./src/components/*16* | sed -e 's/\.\/src\/components\///' | sed -e 's/\..*$//' | sed -e 's/\(.*\)/\1,/' >> ./example/icon16.tsx && cat ./example/exampleMiddle.tsx >> ./example/icon16.tsx && ls -1 ./src/components/*16* | sed -e 's/\.\/src\/components\///' | sed -e 's/\..*$//' | sed -e 's/\(.*\)/\<\1\/\>/' >> ./example/icon16.tsx && cat ./example/exampleEnd.tsx >> ./example/icon16.tsx
